data.description: Range price. Seller will accept/counter offers from $400,000-$410,000. Enjoy magnificent mountain & desert views from this gorgeous 2732 sq ft home nestled near the top of the cul-de-sac.  Expansive back yard and no homes behind. Top-selling floorplan features 4BR/2.5BA plus an upstairs LOFT & downstairs DEN -- ideal for guests or home office. Spacious living area seamlessly flows into gourmet kitchen with 42'' Timberlake cabinets, Quartz countertops, lrg island, gas range & SS appliances. French door referigerator stays! 9-ft ceilings & tasteful 18'' ceramic tile floors downstairs. Located in the foothills of the scenic Santa Rita Mountains, this peaceful community is away from the hustle and bustle yet has easy access to I-10 & major employment centers. Top rated Vail School District.
